(4, 'Giới thiệu về chúng tôi', '1', 1617287975, '<h1><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;\">ISmart</span> &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c ph&aacute;t tri&aacute;&raquo;&fnof;n t&aacute;&raquo;&laquo; m&aacute;&raquo;&trade;t c&aacute;&raquo;&shy;a h&agrave;ng s&aacute;&raquo;&shy;a ch&aacute;&raquo;&macr;a &Auml;&lsquo;i&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;n tho&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i nh&aacute;&raquo; l&aacute;&ordm;&raquo; 10 n&Auml;&fnof;m v&aacute;&raquo; tr&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;c. Qua qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh ph&aacute;t tri&aacute;&raquo;&fnof;n &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;n nay &Auml;&lsquo;&atilde; tr&aacute;&raquo;&Yuml; th&agrave;nh 1 si&ecirc;u th&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo; &Auml;&lsquo;i&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;n m&aacute;y&nbsp;mua b&aacute;n&nbsp;&Auml;&lsquo;i&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;n tho&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i, laptop&nbsp;uy t&iacute;n t&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i qu&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n T&acirc;n B&igrave;nh,&nbsp;th&agrave;nh ph&aacute;&raquo;&lsquo; H&aacute;&raquo;&ldquo; Ch&iacute; Minh</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://vnn-imgs-f.vgcloud.vn/2020/08/22/10/sieu-thi-dien-may-1.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><em>To&agrave;n c&aacute;&ordm;&pound;nh b&ecirc;n trong si&ecirc;u th&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo; &Auml;&lsquo;i&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;n m&aacute;y ISmart</em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">V&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;i tinh th&aacute;&ordm;&sect;n c&aacute;&ordm;&sect;u th&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo;, ham h&aacute;&raquo;c h&aacute;&raquo;i, li&ecirc;n t&aacute;&raquo;&yen;c thay &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&bull;i. <span style=\"color:#ff0000;\">ISmart&nbsp;</span>&Auml;&lsquo;&atilde; x&acirc;y d&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn;ng v&Auml;&fnof;n h&oacute;a ph&aacute;&raquo;&yen;c v&aacute;&raquo;&yen; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng v&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;t tr&aacute;&raquo;&trade;i v&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;i slogan &quot; Ti&ecirc;n phong s&aacute;&raquo;&copy; m&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;nh ph&aacute;&raquo;&yen; v&aacute;&raquo;&yen;/N&acirc;ng t&aacute;&ordm;&sect;m gi&aacute; tr&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng &quot;, lu&ocirc;n &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&middot;t kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng l&agrave;m trung t&acirc;m trong m&aacute;&raquo;i suy ngh&Auml;&copy; v&agrave; h&agrave;nh &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&trade;ng c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a m&igrave;nh. <span style=\"color:#ff0000;\">ISmart</span> &Auml;&lsquo;&atilde; n&aacute;&raquo;&mdash; l&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn;c x&acirc;y d&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn;ng m&aacute;&raquo;&trade;t &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&trade;i ng&Aring;&copy; nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n lu&ocirc;n t&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n t&acirc;m ph&aacute;&raquo;&yen;c v&aacute;&raquo;&yen; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Khi mua s&aacute;&ordm;&macr;m t&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i si&ecirc;u th&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo;, kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s&aacute;&ordm;&frac12; &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n t&AElig;&deg; v&aacute;&ordm;&yen;n chuy&ecirc;n s&acirc;u, &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo;nh h&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;ng l&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn;a ch&aacute;&raquo;n s&aacute;&ordm;&pound;n ph&aacute;&ordm;&copy;m ph&ugrave; h&aacute;&raquo;&pound;p nh&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t v&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;i nhu c&aacute;&ordm;&sect;u s&aacute;&raquo;&shy; d&aacute;&raquo;&yen;ng v&agrave; t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh. M&aacute;&raquo;&yen;c ti&ecirc;u cu&aacute;&raquo;&lsquo;i c&ugrave;ng l&agrave; mang l&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i nh&aacute;&raquo;&macr;ng th&ocirc;ng tin th&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn;c s&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn; kh&aacute;ch quan, ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c nh&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t v&agrave; s&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn; tho&aacute;&ordm;&pound;i m&aacute;i v&agrave; h&agrave;i l&ograve;ng cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng khi l&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn;a ch&aacute;&raquo;n mua h&agrave;ng. Si&ecirc;u th&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo; c&Aring;&copy;ng &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&middot;c bi&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;t d&agrave;nh nhi&aacute;&raquo;u ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch &AElig;&deg;u &Auml;&lsquo;&atilde;i ch&Auml;&fnof;m s&oacute;c cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng th&acirc;n thi&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;t, g&aacute;&ordm;&macr;n b&oacute;.&nbsp;N&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;u qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; b&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t k&aacute;&raquo;&sup3; th&aacute;&ordm;&macr;c m&aacute;&ordm;&macr;c ho&aacute;&ordm;&middot;c nghi ng&aacute;&raquo; n&agrave;o<b><i>,</i></b>&nbsp;&Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;u c&oacute; th&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; y&ecirc;u c&aacute;&ordm;&sect;u &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&bull;i tr&aacute;&ordm;&pound; h&agrave;ng trong v&ograve;ng 10 ng&agrave;y.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Files/2019/04/08/1159513/Gallery/sieu-thi-dien-may-xanh-260-cau-giay-ha-noi8.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><em>Nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n t&AElig;&deg; v&aacute;&ordm;&yen;n kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng</em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">S&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn; n&aacute;&raquo;&mdash; l&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn;c c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a<span style=\"color:#ff0000;\"> ISmart</span>&nbsp;&Auml;&lsquo;&atilde; &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;n &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;p b&aacute;&ordm;&plusmn;ng s&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn; tin y&ecirc;u v&agrave; &aacute;&raquo;&sect;ng h&aacute;&raquo;&trade; t&aacute;&raquo;&laquo; ph&iacute;a kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng qua c&aacute;c l&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;t tham quan mua s&aacute;&ordm;&macr;m &aacute;&raquo;&bull;n &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo;nh v&agrave; lu&ocirc;n t&Auml;&fnof;ng tr&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&Yuml;ng trong su&aacute;&raquo;&lsquo;t nh&aacute;&raquo;&macr;ng n&Auml;&fnof;m v&aacute;&raquo;&laquo;a qua. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh giao d&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo;ch s&aacute;&ordm;&frac12; v&aacute;&ordm;&laquo;n kh&ocirc;ng th&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; tr&aacute;nh kh&aacute;&raquo;i nh&aacute;&raquo;&macr;ng thi&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;u s&oacute;t r&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t mong nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c &yacute; ki&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;n &Auml;&lsquo;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p ch&acirc;n th&agrave;nh t&aacute;&raquo;&laquo; ph&iacute;a qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; <span style=\"color:#ff0000;\">ISmart</span>&nbsp;ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng ho&agrave;n thi&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;n h&AElig;&iexcl;n.Xin c&aacute;&ordm;&pound;m &AElig;&iexcl;n</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),
(5, 'Câu hỏi thường gặp', '2', 1617289014, '<h1><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maydongphucglu.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/giai_dap_thac_mac_0.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto;\" /></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><em><b>H&aacute;&raquo;i:</b></em>&nbsp;<font color=\"#0000FF\">Gi&aacute; s&aacute;&ordm;&pound;n ph&aacute;&ordm;&copy;m b&aacute;n t&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i &Auml;i&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;n m&aacute;y ISmart&nbsp;&Auml;&lsquo;&atilde; bao g&aacute;&raquo;&ldquo;m thu&aacute;&ordm;&iquest; VAT ch&AElig;&deg;a?</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><em><b>&Auml;&aacute;p:</b></em>&nbsp;T&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t c&aacute;&ordm;&pound; s&aacute;&ordm;&pound;n ph&aacute;&ordm;&copy;m b&aacute;n t&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i ISmart&nbsp;&Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;u &Auml;&lsquo;&atilde; bao g&aacute;&raquo;&ldquo;m thu&aacute;&ordm;&iquest; VAT.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><em><b>H&aacute;&raquo;i:</b></em>&nbsp;<font color=\"#0000FF\">L&agrave;m sao bi&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;t &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&iexcl;n &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&middot;t h&agrave;ng th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng?</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b>&Auml;&aacute;p:</b>&nbsp;Khi &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&middot;t h&agrave;ng th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s&aacute;&ordm;&frac12; nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c email th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o x&aacute;c nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n chi ti&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;t &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&iexcl;n h&agrave;ng. Trong v&ograve;ng 24 ti&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;ng nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n g&aacute;&raquo;i &Auml;&lsquo;i&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;n cho qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; x&aacute;c nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&iexcl;n h&agrave;ng.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b>Ghi ch&uacute;:</b>&nbsp;&Auml;&aacute;&raquo;&lsquo;i v&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;i &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&iexcl;n &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&middot;t h&agrave;ng online trong gi&aacute;&raquo; h&aacute;nh ch&iacute;nh th&igrave; ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i s&aacute;&ordm;&frac12; li&ecirc;n h&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger; ngay trong ng&agrave;y. &Auml;&aacute;&ordm;&middot;t h&agrave;ng sau 5h chi&aacute;&raquo;u th&igrave; ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i s&aacute;&ordm;&frac12; li&ecirc;n h&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger; v&agrave;o s&aacute;ng h&ocirc;m sau. &Auml;&aacute;&ordm;&middot;t h&agrave;ng sau 5h chi&aacute;&raquo;u th&aacute;&raquo;&copy; 7 v&agrave; ng&agrave;y ch&aacute;&raquo;&sect; nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;t th&igrave; li&ecirc;n h&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger; v&agrave;o s&aacute;ng th&aacute;&raquo;&copy; 2 tu&aacute;&ordm;&sect;n sau.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><em><b>H&aacute;&raquo;i:</b></em><font color=\"#0000FF\">L&agrave;m sao t&ocirc;i &nbsp;bi&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;t &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c khi n&agrave;o s&aacute;&ordm;&frac12; giao h&agrave;ng t&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;i n&AElig;&iexcl;i?</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b>&Auml;&aacute;p:</b>&nbsp;Tr&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;c khi giao h&agrave;ng nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n giao nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a ISmart&nbsp;s&aacute;&ordm;&frac12; li&ecirc;n h&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger; v&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;i qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng tr&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;c 15 ho&aacute;&ordm;&middot;c 30 ph&uacute;t.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><em><b>H&aacute;&raquo;i:</b></em>&nbsp;<font color=\"#0000FF\">Khi nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n h&agrave;ng c&oacute; ph&aacute;&ordm;&pound;i l&agrave;m th&aacute;&raquo;&sect; t&aacute;&raquo;&yen;c g&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng?</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b>&Auml;&aacute;p:</b>&nbsp;C&oacute;. Khi nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n h&agrave;ng qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch ph&aacute;&ordm;&pound;i ki&aacute;&raquo;&fnof;m tra k&aacute;&raquo;&sup1; h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a, gi&aacute;&ordm;&yen;y b&aacute;&ordm;&pound;o h&agrave;nh, ph&aacute;&raquo;&yen; ki&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;n v&agrave; qu&agrave; t&aacute;&ordm;&middot;ng k&egrave;m theo&hellip; v&agrave; k&yacute; x&aacute;c nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n. N&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;u ph&aacute;t hi&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;n b&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t k&aacute;&raquo;&sup3; l&aacute;&raquo;&mdash;i s&aacute;&ordm;&pound;n ph&aacute;&ordm;&copy;m hay sai s&oacute;t g&igrave; th&igrave; ph&aacute;&ordm;&pound;i b&aacute;o ngay cho nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n giao nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n ho&aacute;&ordm;&middot;c nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; x&aacute;&raquo;&shy; l&yacute; k&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo;p th&aacute;&raquo;i.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><em><b>H&aacute;&raquo;i:</b></em>&nbsp;<font color=\"#0000FF\">Khi &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&middot;t h&agrave;ng th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng th&igrave; trong bao l&acirc;u s&aacute;&ordm;&frac12; nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c h&agrave;ng?</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b>&Auml;&aacute;p:</b>&nbsp;&Auml;&aacute;&raquo;&lsquo;i v&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;i c&aacute;c khu v&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn;c trung t&acirc;m g&aacute;&ordm;&sect;n chi nh&aacute;nh c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a si&ecirc;u th&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo; ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i s&aacute;&ordm;&frac12; giao h&agrave;ng trong ng&agrave;y, c&ograve;n &aacute;&raquo;&Yuml; xa trung t&acirc;m c&oacute; th&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; giao h&agrave;ng trong v&ograve;ng 1 &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;n 2 ng&agrave;y. C&aacute;c t&aacute;&raquo;&permil;nh th&agrave;nh l&acirc;n c&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n giao h&agrave;ng t&aacute;&raquo;&laquo; 3 &ndash; 5.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b>L&AElig;&deg;u &yacute;:</b>&nbsp;Trong nh&aacute;&raquo;&macr;ng ng&agrave;y c&oacute; ch&AElig;&deg;&AElig;&iexcl;ng tr&igrave;nh KM l&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;n th&igrave; th&aacute;&raquo;i gian giao h&agrave;ng c&oacute; th&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; ch&aacute;&ordm;&shy;m h&AElig;&iexcl;n b&igrave;nh th&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;ng do s&aacute;&raquo;&lsquo; l&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;ng &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&iexcl;n &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&middot;t h&agrave;ng nhi&aacute;&raquo;u. &Auml;&aacute;&ordm;&middot;c bi&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;t, n&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;u qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; nhu c&aacute;&ordm;&sect;u giao h&agrave;ng g&aacute;&ordm;&yen;p ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i c&oacute; th&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; &AElig;&deg;u ti&ecirc;n giao h&agrave;ng li&aacute;&raquo;n cho qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><em><b>H&aacute;&raquo;i:&nbsp;</b></em><font color=\"#0000FF\">T&ocirc;i mu&aacute;&raquo;&lsquo;n thay &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&bull;i &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo;a ch&aacute;&raquo;&permil; nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n h&agrave;ng c&oacute; &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c kh&ocirc;ng?</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b>&Auml;&aacute;p:</b>&nbsp;&Auml;&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c. N&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;u qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch mua h&agrave;ng online th&igrave; h&atilde;y li&ecirc;n h&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger; ngay v&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;i t&aacute;&raquo;&bull;ng &Auml;&lsquo;&agrave;i t&AElig;&deg; v&aacute;&ordm;&yen;n b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng (08) 3856 3388, c&ograve;n mua tr&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn;c ti&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;p t&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i qu&aacute;&ordm;&sect;y th&igrave; li&ecirc;n h&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger; t&aacute;&raquo;&bull;ng &Auml;&lsquo;&agrave;i (08) 3950 5060 &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i c&aacute;&ordm;&shy;p nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;t. Tr&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;c khi giao h&agrave;ng nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n giao nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n s&aacute;&ordm;&frac12; g&aacute;&raquo;i &Auml;&lsquo;i&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;n cho qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch x&aacute;c nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n th&aacute;&raquo;i gian v&agrave; &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo;a ch&aacute;&raquo;&permil; giao h&agrave;ng l&aacute;&ordm;&sect;n cu&aacute;&raquo;&lsquo;i.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><em><b>H&aacute;&raquo;i:</b></em>&nbsp;<font color=\"#0000FF\">T&ocirc;i l&agrave; ng&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;i mua h&agrave;ng nh&AElig;&deg;ng khi giao h&agrave;ng t&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;i n&AElig;&iexcl;i m&agrave; t&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng &aacute;&raquo;&Yuml; nh&agrave; th&igrave; nh&AElig;&deg; th&aacute;&ordm;&iquest; n&agrave;o?</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b>&Auml;&aacute;p:</b>&nbsp;Trong tr&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;ng h&aacute;&raquo;&pound;p qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch kh&ocirc;ng &aacute;&raquo;&Yuml; nh&agrave; th&igrave; c&oacute; th&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; nh&aacute;&raquo; ng&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;i th&acirc;n trong nh&agrave; k&yacute; nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n s&aacute;&ordm;&pound;n ph&aacute;&ordm;&copy;m. Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; l&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i t&ecirc;n v&agrave; s&aacute;&raquo;&lsquo; &Auml;&lsquo;i&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;n tho&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a ng&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;i nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n h&agrave;ng th&aacute;&ordm;&iquest; &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n ti&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;n li&ecirc;n l&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;c khi giao h&agrave;ng &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;n.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><em><b>H&aacute;&raquo;i:&nbsp;</b></em><font color=\"#0000FF\">C&aacute;c h&igrave;nh th&aacute;&raquo;&copy;c thanh to&aacute;n khi &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&middot;t h&agr