ve;nh, Tp. HCM.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><em><b>H&aacute;&raquo;i:</b></em>&nbsp;<font color=\"#0000FF\">N&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;u h&agrave;ng b&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo; l&aacute;&raquo;&mdash;i, h&AElig;&deg; h&aacute;&raquo;ng, tr&aacute;&ordm;&sect;y x&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;c ho&aacute;&ordm;&middot;c kh&ocirc;ng &Auml;&lsquo;&uacute;ng m&atilde; s&aacute;&ordm;&pound;n ph&aacute;&ordm;&copy;m &Auml;&lsquo;&atilde; &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&middot;t th&igrave; nh&AElig;&deg; th&aacute;&ordm;&iquest; n&agrave;o?</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b>&Auml;&aacute;p:</b>&nbsp;Trong v&ograve;ng 3 ng&agrave;y k&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; t&aacute;&raquo;&laquo; khi qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n h&agrave;ng n&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;u s&aacute;&ordm;&pound;n ph&aacute;&ordm;&copy;m b&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo; tr&aacute;&raquo;&yen;c tr&aacute;&ordm;&middot;c do l&aacute;&raquo;&mdash;i k&aacute;&raquo;&sup1; thu&aacute;&ordm;&shy;t c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a nh&agrave; s&aacute;&ordm;&pound;n xu&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t ho&aacute;&ordm;&middot;c kh&ocirc;ng &Auml;&lsquo;&uacute;ng m&atilde; s&aacute;&ordm;&pound;n ph&aacute;&ordm;&copy;m do l&aacute;&raquo;&mdash;i c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a ISmart, s&aacute;&ordm;&pound;n ph&aacute;&ordm;&copy;m s&aacute;&ordm;&frac12; &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c b&aacute;&ordm;&pound;o h&agrave;nh, &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&bull;i ho&aacute;&ordm;&middot;c tr&aacute;&ordm;&pound; l&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i. Th&aacute;&raquo;i gian &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&bull;i tr&aacute;&ordm;&pound; h&agrave;ng cho qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t&aacute;&raquo;&laquo; 1 &ndash; 3 ng&agrave;y. Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; th&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; g&aacute;&raquo;i (08) 3950 5060 &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c h&aacute;&raquo;&mdash; tr&aacute;&raquo;&pound; t&aacute;&raquo;&lsquo;t nh&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><em><b>H&aacute;&raquo;i:</b></em>&nbsp;<font color=\"#0000FF\">&Auml;i&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;n m&aacute;y ISmart&nbsp;c&oacute; giao h&agrave;ng &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;n t&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n n&AElig;&iexcl;i kh&ocirc;ng? Ph&iacute; v&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n chuy&aacute;&raquo;&fnof;n t&iacute;nh nh&AElig;&deg; th&aacute;&ordm;&iquest; n&agrave;o?</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b>&Auml;&aacute;p:</b>&nbsp;ISmart&nbsp;giao h&agrave;ng tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n qu&aacute;&raquo;&lsquo;c. N&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;u qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch &aacute;&raquo;&Yuml; xa c&aacute;c qu&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n trung t&acirc;m TP.HCM ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i t&iacute;nh ph&iacute; giao nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n t&ugrave;y theo t&aacute;&raquo;&laquo;ng khu v&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn;c theo b&aacute;&ordm;&pound;ng ph&iacute; v&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n chuy&aacute;&raquo;&fnof;n c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a c&ocirc;ng ty.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><em><b>H&aacute;&raquo;i:&nbsp;</b></em><font color=\"#0000FF\">Ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch b&aacute;&ordm;&pound;o h&agrave;nh c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a ISmart&nbsp;nh&AElig;&deg; th&aacute;&ordm;&iquest; n&agrave;o?</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b>&Auml;&aacute;p:&nbsp;</b>T&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t c&aacute;&ordm;&pound; s&aacute;&ordm;&pound;n ph&aacute;&ordm;&copy;m mua t&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i ISmart&nbsp;&Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;u &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c b&aacute;&ordm;&pound;o h&agrave;nh ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng. T&ugrave;y t&aacute;&raquo;&laquo;ng l&aacute;&raquo;&mdash;i s&aacute;&ordm;&pound;n ph&aacute;&ordm;&copy;m m&agrave; ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i c&oacute; th&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;n b&aacute;&ordm;&pound;o h&agrave;nh t&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n nh&agrave; ho&aacute;&ordm;&middot;c &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&deg;a s&aacute;&ordm;&pound;n ph&aacute;&ordm;&copy;m &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;n H&atilde;ng ho&aacute;&ordm;&middot;c &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;n si&ecirc;u th&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo; &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; b&aacute;&ordm;&pound;o h&agrave;nh. Ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch n&agrave;y &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c &aacute;p d&aacute;&raquo;&yen;ng cho t&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t c&aacute;&ordm;&pound; qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng &aacute;&raquo;&Yuml; n&aacute;&raquo;&trade;i th&agrave;nh v&agrave; ngo&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i th&agrave;nh. M&aacute;&raquo;i v&aacute;&ordm;&yen;n &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo; li&ecirc;n quan &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;n b&aacute;&ordm;&pound;o h&agrave;nh Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng li&ecirc;n h&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger; v&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;i ISmart&nbsp;&Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; &Auml;&lsquo;&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c h&aacute;&raquo;&mdash; tr&aacute;&raquo;&pound; b&aacute;&ordm;&pound;o h&agrave;nh t&aacute;&raquo;&lsquo;t nh&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><em><b>H&aacute;&raquo;i:&nbsp;</b></em><font color=\"#0000FF\">Th&aacute;&raquo;i gian l&agrave;m vi&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;c c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a si&ecirc;u th&aacute;&raquo;&lsaquo; ISmart&nbsp;nh&AElig;&deg; th&aacute;&ordm;&iquest; n&agrave;o?</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b>&Auml;&aacute;p:</b>&nbsp;ISmart&nbsp;m&aacute;&raquo;&Yuml; c&aacute;&raquo;&shy;a ph&aacute;&raquo;&yen;c v&aacute;&raquo;&yen; qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng 7 ng&agrave;y tr&ecirc;n tu&aacute;&ordm;&sect;n, k&aacute;&raquo;&fnof; c&aacute;&ordm;&pound; ng&agrave;y l&aacute;&raquo;&hellip; v&agrave; ch&aacute;&raquo;&sect; nh&aacute;&ordm;&shy;t (Tr&aacute;&raquo;&laquo; T&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;t Nguy&ecirc;n &Auml;&aacute;n)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Th&aacute;&raquo;i gian l&agrave;m vi&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;c &Auml;&lsquo;&aacute;&raquo;&lsquo;i v&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;i nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n t&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i qu&aacute;&ordm;&sect;y l&agrave; 8h30&rsquo; &ndash; 21h30&rsquo; t&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t c&aacute;&ordm;&pound; c&aacute;c ng&agrave;y trong tu&aacute;&ordm;&sect;n.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Th&aacute;&raquo;i gian l&agrave;m vi&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;c c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a b&aacute;&raquo;&trade; ph&aacute;&ordm;&shy;n b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng online:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\">Th&aacute;&raquo;&copy; 2 &ndash; CN: L&agrave;m vi&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;c t&aacute;&raquo;&laquo; 8h30 &ndash; 21h00&rsquo;</span></b></span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b>Ngo&agrave;i ra, n&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;u Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&aacute;&ordm;&sect;n th&ocirc;ng tin ho&aacute;&ordm;&middot;c c&oacute; b&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t c&aacute;&raquo;&copy; th&aacute;&ordm;&macr;c m&aacute;&ordm;&macr;c n&agrave;o vui l&ograve;ng g&aacute;&raquo;&shy;i t&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;i email:&nbsp;</b><a href=\"mailto:online@dienmaycholon.com.vn\">online@dienmayISmart.com.vn</a><b>. Nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n &Auml;i&aacute;&raquo;&Dagger;n M&aacute;y ISmart&nbsp;s&aacute;&ordm;&frac12; t&AElig;&deg; v&aacute;&ordm;&yen;n cho qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch trong th&aacute;&raquo;i gian s&aacute;&raquo;&rsaquo;m nh&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t. Xin c&aacute;&ordm;&pound;m &AElig;&iexcl;n!</b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n');

